HEADWORD: Pill
<hw>Pill</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. <er>Peel</er> skin,
or <er>Pillion</er>.]</ety> <def>The peel or skin.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> ⟦ldquo⟧Some be covered over with crusts, or hard
<xex>pills</xex>, as the locusts.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Holland.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
